column1: Wang, Jian Rang, Tony Letchford, Phil Comeau, and J.P Kimmins. “Above- and Below-ground Biomass and Nutrient Distribution of a Paper Birch and Subalpine Fir Mixed-species Stand in the Sub-Boreal Spruce Zone of British Columbia.” Forest Ecology and Management 130, no. 1–3 (May 1, 2000): 17–26. doi:10.1016/S0378-1127(99)00193-0.
